♪ When you come rushing back still ♪

838
00:38:33,950 --> 00:38:36,320
♪ The young you ♪

839
00:38:47,280 --> 00:38:47,960
Xiaoman.

840
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:51,240
Your flowers are growing really well.

841
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:56,560
What's today's date?

842
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:57,550
The 7th.

843
00:38:58,920 --> 00:39:02,450
The 7th, 8th, and 9th are the dates of the
college entrance exam.

844
00:39:05,960 --> 00:39:07,210
It's the 7th.

845
00:39:13,670 --> 00:39:17,110
I have two friends taking the exam today.

846
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:21,110
I hope they do well.

847
00:39:41,480 --> 00:39:43,010
Still got time to space out?

848
00:39:52,170 --> 00:39:53,720
[East Integrated Chemical Plant]

849
00:39:54,880 --> 00:39:56,480
Is it ready, Mom? I'm hungry.

850
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:58,000
Coming.

851
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,880
Matsutake chicken soup.

852
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:02,760
We were just waiting for you.

853
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:03,920
It's piping hot.

854
00:40:04,530 --> 00:40:05,590
It smells amazing.

855
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:07,550
-It looks…
-Careful, it's hot.

856
00:40:07,550 --> 00:40:08,360
Are there any other dishes?

857
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:09,000
No.

858
00:40:09,070 --> 00:40:10,320
Alright, let's eat.

859
00:40:10,320 --> 00:40:10,760
Okay.

860
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,760
Let me say a few words.

861
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,480
It's been over a year.

862
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:19,480
The hardest working person in our family

863
00:40:19,480 --> 00:40:21,110
has to be our daughter, right?

864
00:40:21,110 --> 00:40:21,550
Right.

865
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:25,110
Preparing for the college entrance exam
this past year

866
00:40:25,110 --> 00:40:27,000
has really worn her out.

867
00:40:27,920 --> 00:40:29,550
So today, your mom specially made

868
00:40:29,550 --> 00:40:31,150
your most favourite soup.

869
00:40:31,600 --> 00:40:32,820
She spent half the day making it.

870
00:40:32,820 --> 00:40:35,370
Yes, I started stewing it
since the afternoon.

871
00:40:35,370 --> 00:40:36,580
Serve her the first bowl.

872
00:40:36,580 --> 00:40:37,920
Right. Come here, sweetie.

873
00:40:37,920 --> 00:40:38,760
Drink up.

874
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:40,080
Nourish your body.

875
00:40:40,110 --> 00:40:42,360
You've worked hard this year.

876
00:40:43,360 --> 00:40:45,150
It smells so good and so fresh.

877
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:50,070
Careful, it's hot. Watch out.

878
00:40:50,550 --> 00:40:51,110
Okay.

879
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:52,960
Come, give it a taste.

880
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:53,360
Okay.

881
00:40:53,550 --> 00:40:54,540
Yan, let me serve you some.

882
00:40:54,540 --> 00:40:55,030
No, wait.

883
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:56,630
I'll have a sip of wine first.

884
00:40:58,760 --> 00:40:59,890
Smells good, right?

885
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:01,400
Hot! It's so hot.

886
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:02,630
It's delicious.

887
00:41:02,630 --> 00:41:04,030
Take it easy.

888
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:07,800
Dad,

889
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:10,250
I'm going to Xia Lei's house after dinner.

890
00:41:11,030 --> 00:41:11,760
That's good.

891
00:41:11,920 --> 00:41:13,780
While your memory is still fresh,

892
00:41:13,840 --> 00:41:15,640
check your answers with Xia Lei.

893
00:41:17,350 --> 00:41:18,480
Check what answers?

894
00:41:18,510 --> 00:41:20,880
I've already submitted
my college applications.

895
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:22,420
Then what are you going there for?

896
00:41:22,420 --> 00:41:23,760
We're going to see Xiaoman tomorrow.

897
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:26,160
I want to discuss with Xia Lei
what to bring.

898
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:28,950
What's the rush?

899
00:41:29,650 --> 00:41:30,570
Dad promised

900
00:41:30,590 --> 00:41:32,650
he'd take me to see him after the exam.

901
00:41:33,130 --> 00:41:35,260
Right. Mom, get a thermos ready for me.

902
00:41:37,040 --> 00:41:37,690
Yan,

903
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:40,610
I think something is wrong with this soup.

904
00:41:42,840 --> 00:41:44,550
What's wrong with the soup?
It tastes fine to me.

905
00:41:44,550 --> 00:41:45,810
Your mom is the expert.

906
00:41:45,830 --> 00:41:46,670
Let's listen to her.

907
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:47,550
I'll go check.

908
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:52,360
Is it too salty or something?

909
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:57,760
Are you really taking her to
the juvenile detention center tomorrow?

910
00:41:57,760 --> 00:41:59,290
I'd forgotten all about it.

911
00:42:00,050 --> 00:42:01,700
But I did promise her,

912
00:42:02,030 --> 00:42:03,280
so I have to go.

913
00:42:03,550 --> 00:42:04,630
What should we do?

914
00:42:05,190 --> 00:42:06,990
It's been so long since they met.

915
00:42:07,070 --> 00:42:08,490
If they see each other again

916
00:42:08,490 --> 00:42:10,150
and those feelings come back,

917
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,280
what should we do?

918
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:13,590
Don't worry.

919
00:42:13,760 --> 00:42:14,880
Don't let her go.

920
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:15,670
Let me think.

921
00:42:16,160 --> 00:42:17,780
Don't take her there tomorrow.

922
00:42:17,780 --> 00:42:19,050
Don't take her.

923
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:21,920
Why go to a place like that?

924
00:42:22,360 --> 00:42:23,420
Let's go back first

925
00:42:24,360 --> 00:42:25,820
or she'll get suspicious.

926
00:42:26,740 --> 00:42:28,740
[Tiecheng Juvenile Correctional Facility]

927
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:31,360
Officer Li, Officer Li?

928
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:34,070
Officer Li?

929
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:36,980
Officer Li.

930
00:42:37,920 --> 00:42:38,550
What is it?

931
00:42:39,320 --> 00:42:41,110
Well, I wanted to ask,

932
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:43,360
did anyone come to see me today?

933
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:45,690
Didn't your uncle just come
a few days ago?

934
00:42:46,070 --> 00:42:48,330
Well, the college entrance exam is over.

935
00:42:48,710 --> 00:42:50,110
Didn't any of my classmates come?

936
00:42:50,110 --> 00:42:52,550
Only immediate family members

937
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:54,230
or guardians can visit.

938
00:42:54,230 --> 00:42:55,510
Classmates can't come?

939
00:42:55,510 --> 00:42:56,210
No.

940
00:42:58,580 --> 00:43:00,580
Your flower is growing really well.

941
00:43:02,060 --> 00:43:02,870
Get some rest.
